p.k: While playing a fantasy adventure game the Titans are transported inside and must find the key to return home. / Raven teaches the other Titans how to dance properly but soon they are captured by the Dance Demon. / The Titans reminisce about a surprise party. / The Titans try to remember how to be superheroes in order to stop The Brain. / When the gang breaks Robin's beloved staff, Robin is forced to find a replacement.
